'''辅助病毒'''（英文：Helper virus），是一种能够辅助另一种本身有缺陷病毒进行复制的[[病毒|病毒]]。<ref>{{Cite web|title=helper virus|url=https://www.oxfordreference.com/view/10.1093/oi/authority.20110803095929684|accessdate=2021-04-02|work=Oxford Reference|language=en}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=helper virus|url=https://medical-dictionary.thefreedictionary.com/helper+virus|accessdate=2021-04-02|work=TheFreeDictionary.com|archive-date=2016-10-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161021013041/http://medical-dictionary.thefreedictionary.com/helper+virus|dead-url=no}}</ref> 譬如[[丁型肝炎|丁型肝炎病毒]]需要借助感染同一细胞的[[乙型肝炎病毒|乙型肝炎病毒]]才能进行复制。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Helper Virus - an overview|url=https://www.sciencedirect.com/topics/biochemistry-genetics-and-molecular-biology/helper-virus|accessdate=2021-04-02|work=|publisher=ScienceDirect|language=en|archive-date=2021-05-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210505183152/https://www.sciencedirect.com/topics/biochemistry-genetics-and-molecular-biology/helper-virus|dead-url=no}}</ref>此外，在[[基因治療|基因治疗]]中，辅助病毒常被用来复制和传播[[病毒載體|病毒载体]]。<ref>{{cite book|chapter=14 - Immunization Against Viral Diseases|vauthors=Graham BS, Crowe JE, Ledgerwood JE|page=[https://archive.org/details/fieldsvirology0002unse_w7i9/page/n403 403]|title=Fields Virology|url=https://archive.org/details/fieldsvirology0002unse_w7i9|edition=6|veditors=Knipe DM, Howley PM|publisher=Wolters Kluwer Health|date=2007}}</ref>

